CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 30, 1958, pg. 14, reads: "Cooling - Lissome Lucretia Tabb, 2297 Sumner Dr., cools in the summer breezes as she takes her final dip of the season at a local swimming pool.  She claims the stretch on the diving board is relaxing, but the boys say it's eye-filling.  Employed as a typist, the young lady also is a part-time model. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Lucretia Tabb wearing bathing suit and posed on diving board of outdoor swimming pool
